title: Mission Of Hero [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
You are a soldier of an special elite squad. You and the squad are sent to carry out a secret operation, during which you must steal information from the terrorist base. To complete this operation, you are secretly placed on a cargo ship of terrorists. However, the mission is not going according to plan and you are being revealed. Now your mission is to survive! Use for this purpose all your skills, like the ability to move hidden, and the ability to handle all kinds of weapons! Find out what awaits you at the end of the journey.

Features:

- Beautiful realistic graphics.
- Many types of weapons.
- Storyline and various levels.
- Pleasant sound and music.


System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 мmb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 375 mb
